{
  "texts": [
    "For example, it generated names of bisphosphonate drugs when the question was about side effects of bisphosphonates (question 3).",
    "In answer to question 1, it generated a treatment option which is available for cancer (focal therapy) but was not part of the ground truth answer.",
    "PCaMLM and BioGPT responses differed from each other for question 2 and 4, but were still relevant and somewhat appropriate for the question.",
    "Our experiments clearly establish the benefits of developing and employing domain-specific LLMs for sensitive domains like medicine and healthcare, especially for building interactive knowledge dissemination tools.",
    "We plan to expand upon this line of research by developing patient and physician facing chatbots on top of our domain specific LLM for the use case of prostate cancer."
  ]
}